            "Fulcrum",
            "pivot point",
            "between effort and load"
          ]
        },
        {
          "questionText": "Which class of lever has the load in the middle, between the fulcrum and the effort?",
          "answerGuidance": [
            "Class II Lever",
            "Class 2",
            "load in the middle"
          ]
        },
        {
          "questionText": "What mechanical component uses toothed wheels to change the speed or torque of a system?",
